## 6. Configuration Reference

**File:** `configs/pipeline_config.yaml`

```yaml
detector:
  model_name: "yolox-s"         # YOLOX variant
  weights: "weights/yolox.pth"  # Path to custom-trained weights
  input_size: [640, 640]        # Model input resolution (H, W)
  conf_threshold: 0.35          # Min confidence to accept a detection
  nms_threshold: 0.45           # IoU threshold for NMS suppression
  class_names:                  # Class list (must match training order)
    - person
    - dock_open
    - truck
    - dock_closed
    - forklift
    - box_in_hand
    - pallet_load
    - no_truck
  person_class_id: 0            # Which class index = person

tracker:
  track_thresh: 0.45    # Min score to activate a new track
  track_buffer: 90      # Frames to keep a lost track alive (3s @ 30fps)
  match_thresh: 0.85    # IoU threshold for track-detection matching
  frame_rate: 30        # Source video FPS (affects Kalman filter)

reid:
  model_name: "osnet_x1_0"    # OSNet variant
  weights: "weights/osnet.pth" # Optional custom weights (uses pretrained if missing)
  input_size: [256, 128]       # Person crop resize (H, W)
  device: "cuda"               # "cuda" or "cpu"

memory:
  cosine_threshold: 0.72   # Similarity to count as same person (0=anything, 1=identical)
  max_gallery_size: 100    # Maximum distinct persons in gallery
  feature_dim: 512         # Embedding dimension (OSNet output)
  ttl_seconds: 300         # Seconds before an unseen person is removed from gallery
  ema_alpha: 0.25          # EMA weight for gallery update (0=no update, 1=replace)
  max_feats_per_person: 15 # How many raw embeddings to keep per person

api:
  host: "0.0.0.0"   # Bind address for web server
  port: 8000        # Port for web server
```

### Tuning guide

| Goal | Parameter to change |
|---|---|
| Fewer false detections | Raise `conf_threshold` (e.g. 0.40–0.50) |
| More detections (catch far-away people) | Lower `conf_threshold` (e.g. 0.25) |
| Stop losing tracks on fast movement | Raise `track_buffer` (e.g. 120) |
| Same person gets new ID too often | Lower `cosine_threshold` (e.g. 0.60) |
| Different people getting merged | Raise `cosine_threshold` (e.g. 0.78) |
| Person removed from gallery too fast | Raise `ttl_seconds` (e.g. 600) |

